@gtwuser the problem ain't actually in Hudi -- the problem is in Avro converter serializing your schema to JSON (when serializing arrays it creates a wrapper structure for array elements and apparently that clashes with your existing schema.

Would it be possible for you to try more recent Spark and Hudi versions to see if that would resolve an issue for you?

